===Etymology===
From ancient Greek "''autokrates''" "one who governs alone" , from "''autos''" "single, self, same, alone" + "''kratos''" "power".
===Noun===
'''autocracy'''
# form of [[government]] in which unlimited power is held by a single [[individual]]
